{"tid":1660686,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府諗住送退休popo中","createTime":"2019-10-17T15:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T15:54:04.000Z","uid":225818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6442a583fdd80d09a76b991f1e3a5457dded79f1","tid":1660686,"uid":225818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T15:53:51.000Z","msg":"警方發言人稱在警務人員接受利益方面須遵守相關規定<br />\n<br />\n香港警察隊員佐級協會主席林志偉，向會員發信，表示協會聯同政府華員會，與雅居樂集團構建鄰近肇慶東站，具有「港式生活」特色的社區，構建名為「肇慶香港城」。<br />\n<br />\n協會及華員會與雅居樂集團積極磋商，商討細節，並以兩會團購概念，爭取最優惠價格，以提供多一個退休生活的選擇。<br />\n<br />\n警方發言人表示，警務人員在接受利益方面，須遵守《接受利益（行政長官許可）公告》以及有關的《公務員事務規例》、公務員事務局通告、財務通告等的規定。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486830-20191017.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486830-20191017.htm&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaASF8jviwHHlsaTD6zKFHFMM%3D&h=79a12b42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486830-20191017.htm&h=b54002f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486830-20191017.htm</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">呢次我就撐popo啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />為民服務左咁多年 退休一定要比番啲保障佢地 作為愛國為黨既popo隊一定無反對送自己中既理由啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"bf04c2f5daf26f73c99cfdb6825b8e82cea4feb6","tid":1660686,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T15:54:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/afoWPNY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FafoWPNY.jpg&h=041452ea&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"}]}